17 {CRL_REASON_KEY_COMPROMISE, "Key Compromise", "keyCompromise"},

20 "affiliationChanged"},
21 {CRL_REASON_SUPERSEDED, "Superseded", "superseded"},

23 "Cessation Of Operation", "cessationOfOperation"},

32const X509V3_EXT_METHOD v3_crl_reason = {
33 NID_crl_reason, 0, ASN1_ITEM_ref(ASN1_ENUMERATED),
34 0, 0, 0, 0,
35 (X509V3_EXT_I2S)i2s_ASN1_ENUMERATED_TABLE,
36 0,
37 0, 0, 0, 0,
38 crl_reasons
39};
40
41char *i2s_ASN1_ENUMERATED_TABLE(X509V3_EXT_METHOD *method,
42 const ASN1_ENUMERATED *e)
43{
44 ENUMERATED_NAMES *enam;
45 long strval;
46
47 strval = ASN1_ENUMERATED_get(e);
48 for (enam = method->usr_data; enam->lname; enam++) {
49 if (strval == enam->bitnum)
50 return OPENSSL_strdup(enam->lname);
51 }
52 return i2s_ASN1_ENUMERATED(method, e);
53}
